HEADWORD: cyclotron
<hw>cyclotron</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a particle accelerator that
imparts energies of several million electron-volts to rapidly moving
particles; it is used in investigations in nuclear physics and particle
physics.</def>⟦br⟧
